Content Marketing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:8;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"Viral Content Marketing Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/?p=22721\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:617:\"<p>Are you blogger or content marketer? Are you facing difficulty in making your content reach the potential readers? Read this article and get ready to create the right content that will go viral. I was inspired to write this article to help you marketers who are struggling to generate good traffic for your blog or [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/tips-to-create-viral-content-marketing-strategy/\">11 Most Effective Tactics to Make Your Content Go Viral</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Sanjay Dabhoya\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12180:\"<p>Are you blogger or content marketer? Are you facing difficulty in making your content reach the potential readers?</p>\n<p>Read this article and get ready to create the right content that will go viral. I was inspired to write this article to help you marketers who are struggling to generate good traffic for your blog or any other piece of information.</p>\n<p>You can follow these steps and you can also bring more traffic to your information just like any other popular blogger. Ofcourse, It will take some time as there is no shortcut to SEO. You might not see results overnight but if you maintain consistency and follow strategies you will see results.</p>\n<p>Being a content marketer, I had struggled many times to attract potential audience. I can understand the pain of not attracting the audience to the content that took almost 20 to 40 hours of efforts in writing. With years of experience, our team have analysed, what type of content can get attention and what fails. So here we have listed the things that can be useful next time you create a content.</p>\n<p><strong>So, how will you create a content that goes Viral?</strong></p>\n<p>This is very important question and answer is needed. With “VIRAL” I mean the content that is spread quickly or shared with large number of audience. I am sure that many of you are trying to get the answer. By far,  we have concluded few things that will help you to create a shareable content. Lets start then:</p>\n<h3>1. Research</h3>\n<p>Find out what people like around your niche topic in social media channels like <strong>Facebook, Twitter, Google Plus</strong> or any other content channels. Social channels lets you find the live topics discussed among real audience. Read some of those topics and think what type of posts you would like to share or comment. A content should include combination any of the below mentioned perspectives :</p>\n<p>1) Interest<br />\n2) Humor, Sadness<br />\n3) News<br />\n4) Latest Trends<br />\n5) Information<br />\n6) Inspirational<br />\n7) Free downloads<br />\n8) How to and DIY things<br />\n9) Polls and Feedbacks</p>\n<h3>2. Catchy Headlines</h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_27324\" style=\"width: 576px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Catchy-Headlines.gif\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Catchy-Headlines.gif\" alt=\"Catchy Headlines\" width=\"566\" height=\"312\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27324\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Catchy Headlines</p></div>\n<p>8 out of 10 readers will skip reading your content, if your headline is not enough to catch the attention. So without a doubt, headline is the first thing to be taken care of while writing content. This will literally make or break your reader base. You can write headlines in numbered format like:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/top-free-magento-2-themes-extensions/\" target=\"_blank\">Top Free Magento 2 Theme and Extensions For Your Magento Store</a><br />\nOr in a question format like:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/top-free-magento-2-themes-extensions/\" target=\"_blank\">Are You Looking for Free Magento 2 Extensions and Themes?</a></p>\n<h3>3. Invoking Emotions</h3>\n<p>Personally, I have felt that sometimes, I am energised with positive thoughts or posts on any social media channels. You can invoke emotions in your readers with any story that makes them happy or sad after reading your posts. It is very easy to write an informative post, but it takes a bit of creativity to infuse humour or sadness in your content. Our team at Solwin Infotech is skilled with such creativity, just call them and discuss about your topic.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_27331\" style=\"width: 650px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Invoking-Emotions.jpg\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Invoking-Emotions.jpg\" alt=\"Invoking Emotions\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27331\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Invoking-Emotions.jpg 640w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Invoking-Emotions-300x200.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Invoking-Emotions-500x333.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Invoking-Emotions-366x245.jpg 366w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Invoking-Emotions-624x415.jpg 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Invoking Emotions</p></div>\n<h3>4. Be The First One To Announce The News</h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_28579\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Be-The-First-One-To-Announce-The-News.jpeg\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Be-The-First-One-To-Announce-The-News.jpeg\" alt=\"Be The First One To Announce The News\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" class=\"size-full wp-image-28579\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Be-The-First-One-To-Announce-The-News.jpeg 800w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Be-The-First-One-To-Announce-The-News-300x169.jpeg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Be-The-First-One-To-Announce-The-News-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Be-The-First-One-To-Announce-The-News-500x281.jpeg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Be-The-First-One-To-Announce-The-News-624x351.jpeg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Be-The-First-One-To-Announce-The-News-350x197.jpeg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Image source: Buffer.com</p></div>\n<p>Talking about news, I would like to draw your attention regarding the latest news of Demonetization of 500 and 100 Notes in India. Yes, while I am writing this content, our PM has announced the ban on using these high currency notes. If you use <a href=\"https://www.google.com/alerts\" target=\"_blank\">Google news alerts</a> or RSS feeds of any news channels, you will be the first one to pass on the news to local audiences who are unaware of the news. You can create a content using that news and implementing your own opinions and views on that. This way you are catching attention first. You readers will gradually trust your blog as they got to know about something which was shared by you first. They will definitely share your content to their friends and family.</p>\n<p><strong>You can grab such hot topics to write. Creating viral content is quite a difficult  task as it involves open ears and observations to the information and latest trends around you.  But it is not impossible, If you are a good writer. You can also <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">approach us</a> at Solwin Infotech for creating such viral contents. Our content writing services are very affordable.</strong></p>\n<p>Anyway, coming back to our strategies. Remember always, your content can also solve a particular question or problem. If a visitor finds solution with your posts, he/she will definitely come back to your blog. If you or your team are skilled at solving any problems like any technical issues of Lenovo laptops or mobiles. Record a video and share it on <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a>.</p>\n<h3>5. Stay Up-To-Date</h3>\n<p>It is necessary to stay in tune with what is going around. Read and follow other&#8217;s blogs and news around internet. Participate in forums and groups to stay up-to-date with all the latest talks. You can interact, share your views on other&#8217;s posts.</p>\n<h3>6. Which Channel Works For You?</h3>\n<p>Once you start practicing, reading and participating in blogs and forums, you can analyze, which channel helps you to generate visitors. There are so many social channels like Scoopit, Blogs, Reddif, <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SolwinInfotech\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a>, Online magazines etc.. Publish your contents on these channels and check which media is bringing you more and more visitors. You can also do guest blogging and make your content viral. The traffic coming to that blog will be diverted to your post.</p>\n<blockquote><p>We don&#8217;t have a choice on whether we do social media, the question is how well we do it? ― Erik Qualman</p></blockquote>\n<h3>7. Inter-Link Your Posts</h3>\n<p>You can interlink your other channels, once you know which channel is getting you the most traffic. This way you can focus on any specific channel and thus bringing traffic to your other channels. Analyse the list of topics, which attracted more visitors and use its link in other articles.</p>\n<h3>8. Interaction And Communication</h3>\n<p>Using polls and contact forms on your blog is the best way to stay in touch with your audience. Try Solwin Infotech&#8217;s free <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/easy-contact-form-widget-magento-2/\" target=\"_blank\">CONTACT FORM extension</a> on your blog. If you receive any inquiry or feedback from any reader, do not miss to reach them by writing a thank you email to them. Replying your reader&#8217;s comments is also a best way to connect them personally. This way your readers will feel like attended and they will entice to read and comment more on your posts.</p>\n<h3>9. Free Downloads And Resources</h3>\n<p>Free things are always the center of attraction. You can give your readers a link to a free resource which your readers can use it whenever they want. Like for example, A free PDF which can include some tips or tricks of make up for party.</p>\n<h3>10. Use Images</h3>\n<p>You all are very well aware of this saying, “A picture speaks thousand words” Try using a MEME or high definition picture that relates to your content. I have found gif image has been used a lot in almost all contents and articles of 2017. Some stats or graphs like gold price visual might attract your visitors. Visually rich posts is awesome.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_28585\" style=\"width: 582px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/use-of-images.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/use-of-images.png\" alt=\"use of images\" width=\"572\" height=\"619\" class=\"size-full wp-image-28585\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/use-of-images.png 572w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/use-of-images-277x300.png 277w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/use-of-images-500x541.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/use-of-images-185x200.png 185w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Image source: incisive-edge.com</p></div>\n<h3>11. Information</h3>\n<p>Warnings, trends, tips and tricks are some type of information which can entice your readers. Just read and research around internet, magazines and you can share all those informations. Like you can share an informational post regarding an IT FAIR or EXHIBITION about which you read in newspaper last morning. Share your visit experience to any location, you have been recently.</p>\n<p>So, these were some tips to write a creative content. However, not even the news channels or newspapers know, which news or content will be super-hit. So keep trying these things. You may fail several times but you will surely succeed at some point.</p>\n<p><strong>Happy writing <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.2.1/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"🙂\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></strong></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/tips-to-create-viral-content-marketing-strategy/\">11 Most Effective Tactics to Make Your Content Go Viral</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/tips-to-create-viral-content-marketing-strategy/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:47:\"It’s Official – Magento Meetup now @ Surat!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/news/official-magento-meetup-now-surat/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:84:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/news/official-magento-meetup-now-surat/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 09 Jun 2017 13:05:53 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Magento Community\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Magento Meetup\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"Magento Meetup Surat\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"Surat Magento Meetup\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"Surat Magento Meetup Group\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/?p=27434\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:602:\"<p>It was a mere thought until it turned into reality! The Magento Live India 2017 event held at Bengaluru made a lasting impact on our minds as we saw several Magento enthusiasts from different parts of India coming to Bengaluru to learn and know more about the offerings of the Magento community. We strongly felt [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/news/official-magento-meetup-now-surat/\">It&#8217;s Official &#8211; Magento Meetup now @ Surat!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Sanjay Dabhoya\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4734:\"<p>It was a mere thought until it turned into reality!</p>\n<p>The Magento Live India 2017 event held at Bengaluru made a lasting impact on our minds as we saw several Magento enthusiasts from different parts of India coming to Bengaluru to learn and know more about the offerings of the Magento community. We strongly felt that the magnificence of this community should reach to different parts of India.</p>\n<p>However, the seeds of developing local platforms for Magento were sown during the Magento Live India 2017 &#8216;Pre-event meet&#8217; where few of us were casually discussing with some of the Senior Magento team members and community members like Sherrie Rohde (Community Manager), Max Yekaterynenko (Director of Community Engineering), Eugene Tulika (Evangelist), Oleksii Korshenko (Software Architect), Talesh Seeparsan, Ramesh Kumar, Vijay Golani and few others about the idea of expanding the Magento community to different parts of India. Little did we know, that it was going to turn into reality so soon.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">A bunch of us are seated outside the Library Bar at Leela Palace for a Pre <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/MLIN17?src=hash\">#MLIN17</a> hangout. Come drop by. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/realmagento?src=hash\">#realmagento</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/vrfvSGkqK1\">pic.twitter.com/vrfvSGkqK1</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Talesh Seeparsan (@_Talesh) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/_Talesh/status/859023791489507329\">May 1, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>Solwin Infotech takes pleasure in announcing that Surat city is the latest to join the wagon of setting up Magento Meetup groups in different cities of India. Surat now has a Magento Meetup Group of its own. We encourage Magento enthusiasts from Surat and South Gujarat region (Ankaleshwar, Bharuch, Bardoli, Vyara, Navsari, Bilimora, Valsad, Vapi etc) to come and experience the offerings and latest happenings from around the world in Magento. If you are a beginner in Magento, it will surely be a delight for you to learn and know a lot more about Magento. If you are an expert, then you can play the role of a speaker and cascade your knowledge among others. The schedules for events will be released from time to time on the official <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Surat-Magento-Meetup\" target=\"_blank\">Surat Magento Meetup Group</a> page.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Surat-Magento-Meetup-page.png\" alt=\"Surat Magento Meetup page\" width=\"1073\" height=\"702\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-27500\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Surat-Magento-Meetup-page.png 1073w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Surat-Magento-Meetup-page-300x196.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Surat-Magento-Meetup-page-768x502.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Surat-Magento-Meetup-page-1024x670.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Surat-Magento-Meetup-page-500x327.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Surat-Magento-Meetup-page-624x408.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Surat-Magento-Meetup-page-850x556.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Surat-Magento-Meetup-page-306x200.png 306w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1073px) 100vw, 1073px\" /></p>\n<p>This wouldn&#8217;t have been possible without the support of Max Yekaterynenko (Director of Community Engineering), Eugene Tulika (Evangelist) and Taleesh Seeparsan. Special thanks to Sherrie Rohde (Community Manager) for the providing the approval.</p>\n<p>Solwin Infotech is privileged and ready to take this baton ahead in spreading the awareness of the offerings of Magento Community in our city through the Magento Meetup Surat. We think this is a great way of contributing to the Magento community.</p>\n<p>We are 39 members as of now and positive that the number will increase as more and more people become aware about this initiative.</p>\n<p>We think this is great step to strengthen the Magento roots in India. Lets join the Hands and share about <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Surat-Magento-Meetup/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Surat Magento Meetup Group</strong></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/news/official-magento-meetup-now-surat/\">It&#8217;s Official &#8211; Magento Meetup now @ Surat!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/news/official-magento-meetup-now-surat/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"WordPress Version 4.8 Released! Here’s Our Themes Compatibility Report\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5