p=27263\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:658:\"<p>The latest version of WordPress 4.8 has been released yesterday. We make it a priority to always keep our WordPress themes up-to-date, so that our customers can easily switch on latest update of WordPress without any issues. What&#8217;s bundled with WordPress 4.8? WordPress 4.8 adds some great new features to gear up for more intuitive [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/wordpress-4-8-themes-compatibility-report/\">WordPress Version 4.8 Released! Here’s Our Themes Compatibility Report</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Sanjay Dabhoya\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3050:\"<p>The latest version of WordPress 4.8 has been released yesterday. We make it a priority to always keep our WordPress themes up-to-date, so that our customers can easily switch on latest update of WordPress without any issues.</p>\n<h2>What&#8217;s bundled with WordPress 4.8?</h2>\n<p>WordPress 4.8 adds some great new features to gear up for more intuitive WordPress!</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Introduced 3 new widgets &#8211; Image, Video and Audio Widget</li>\n<li>Rich Text Editor with Text Widget</li>\n<li>Link Boundaries update with hyperlinks</li>\n<li>New Admin Dashboard Widget &#8211; WordPress Events and News</li>\n<li>And much more with security updates</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We had started preparation when first RC1 was available and then after we keep updating our themes to be compatible with next WordPress version 4.8. Today, we have published new updates to <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/products/wordpress-themes/\">all of our WordPress themes</a> by taking advantage of the new features WordPress 4.8 offers, both behind the scenes and in the forefront.</p>\n<p>I can confirm that Solwin Infotech&#8217;s every WordPress themes is 100% compatible with WordPress 4.8. There were a few issues that we’ve resolved, though they were very small and unlikely to occur. We have also taken a bit of time to tidy some of the older themes update with latest features in the catalogue.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">WordPress 4.8 “Evans” with community events tie-in, media widgets, improved visual editor,… <a href=\"https://t.co/OkT8mm6ACF\">https://t.co/OkT8mm6ACF</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/m0RFmGoyb9\">pic.twitter.com/m0RFmGoyb9</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; WordPress (@WordPress) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/WordPress/status/872828027683704832\">June 8, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>If you’re interested in reading a bit more on the new bits of WordPress version 4.8, check out the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/2017/06/evans/\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress 4.8</a> Field Guide. As usual, if you run into anything, let me know. Enjoy!</p>\n<h3>Further Reading:</h3>\n<p>So ideally you&#8217;ve discovered some new information today! In case you&#8217;re delighted, I definitely suggest perusing these two articles as well:</p>\n<p>1. <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/super-tips-to-choose-perfect-theme-for-your-wordpress-blog-or-website/\">Tips to Choose Perfect WordPress Theme</a><br />\n2. <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/tips-and-tricks/showcase-your-profile-picture-in-wordpress-website-without-gravatar/\">Showcase Profile Picture in WordPress without Gravatar Account</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/wordpress-4-8-themes-compatibility-report/\">WordPress Version 4.8 Released! Here’s Our Themes Compatibility Report</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/wordpress-4-8-themes-compatibility-report/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"6\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"Magento Live India 2017 – An Experience to Cherish for a Lifetime!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:98:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/ecommerce/magento-live-india-2017-experience-cherish-lifetime/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:107:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/ecommerce/magento-live-india-2017-experience-cherish-lifetime/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s